<div id="ftn25">
<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref25" name="_ftn25" title="" id="_ftn25">[25]</a> Jessica Chen Weiss, “A World Safe for Autocracy?”, <em>Foreign Affairs</em>, July/August 2019, 93, 99, <a href="https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/china/2019-06-11/world-safe-autocracy">https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/china/2019-06-11/world-safe-autocracy</a>.</p>
