<div id="ftn29">
<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref29" name="_ftn29" title="" id="_ftn29">[29]</a> Xi’s ‘China dream’ — China becoming a ‘fully developed nation’ by 2049, the centenary of the founding of the People’s Republic — is clearly contingent on a favourable international context.</p>
