<div id="ftn30">
<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref30" name="_ftn30" title="" id="_ftn30">[30]</a> See Putin interview with the <em>Financial Times</em>, 27 June 2019, <a href="http://en.kremlin.ru/events/president/news/60836">http://en.kremlin.ru/events/president/news/60836</a>.</p>
