<div id="ftn31">
<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref31" name="_ftn31" title="" id="_ftn31">[31]</a> Dmitri Trenin, “The World through Moscow’s Eyes: A Classic Russian Perspective”, <em>The Foreign Service Journal</em>, 3 March 2020, <a href="https://carnegie.ru/2020/03/03/world-through-moscow-s-eyes-classic-russian-perspective-pub-81203">https://carnegie.ru/2020/03/03/world-through-moscow-s-eyes-classic-russian-perspective-pub-81203</a>.</p>
