<div id="ftn34">
<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref34" name="_ftn34" title="" id="_ftn34">[34]</a> Andrei Kolesnikov, “Why Putin’s Rating is at a Record Low”, Carnegie Moscow Center, 11 June 2020, <a href="https://carnegie.ru/commentary/82053">https://carnegie.ru/commentary/82053</a>.</p>
