<p><a href="file://lifile01/userdata/aoliver/Redirection/Desktop/LOWY/BOBO%20LO,%20CHINA%20RUSSIA%20GLOBAL%20ORDER/Bobo%20Lo,%20Global%20Order%20in%20the%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Coronavirus%20-%20China,%20Russia%20and%20the%20West,%20FINAL%20270720.doc#_ftnref37" name="_ftn37" title="" id="_ftn37">[37]</a> See, for example, Vasily Kashin, “Tacit Alliance: Russia and China Take Military Partnership to New Level”, Carnegie Moscow Center, 22 October 2019, <a href="https://carnegie.ru/commentary/80136">https://carnegie.ru/commentary/80136</a>.</p>
